nster, including asking the player what they want to do, handling the run or fight cases.attackMonster() handles the player attacking the monster, including leveling up.attackPlayer() handles the monster attacking the player.Show Solution#include "Random.h" // https://www.learncpp.com/cpp-tutorial/global-random-numbers-random-h/
